      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) equipped with the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This driver-spec example features recent preventative maintenance critical for the chassis, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous response, while the factory limited-slip differential ensures precise torque distribution through the corners. The suspension geometry remains true with upgraded bushings, offering the tactile feedback and balance that define the M-division's peak era. A solid, enthusiast-maintained machine ready for the road.",
